Every @NumAttacks@ attacks, fire an arrow that passes through the current target, dealing @ArrowBaseADDamage*100@% Basic Attack Damage as physical damage, reduced by @ArrowPercentFalloff*100@% per enemy hit.
items.name: The Darkin Bow

items.desc:
The holder gains the Darkin trait.

For every @ManaSpent@ Mana spent, launch a tendril at enemies near the current target, dealing @TFTUnitProperty.trait:TFT_Item_Artifact_DarkinStaff_Damage@ magic damage.

Damage increases based on Stage
items.name: The Darkin Staff

items.desc:
The holder gains the Darkin trait.

Every @TickRate@ seconds, slash adjacent enemies for @SlashADPercent*100@% Basic Attack Damage as physical damage. On takedown or when the holder dashes, slash again.

Dash Cooldown: @DashCooldown@ second
items.name: The Darkin Scythe

items.desc:
Gain @TFTUnitProperty.item:TFT16_Void_PredatorADAP@% Attack Damage and Ability Power. Every @ShedRefresh@ seconds, cleanse crowd control effects and become untargetable for @TFTUnitProperty.item:TFT16_Void_PredatorUntargetableDuration@ second(s).

Recommended users: Rek'Sai and Bel'Veth
items.name: Predator Instincts

items.desc:
Gain @TFTUnitProperty.item:TFT16_Void_AdrenalineModulesDamageAmp@% Damage Amp, increased by @TFTUnitProperty.item:TFT16_Void_AdrenalineModulesDamageAmpPerTick@% after every @AttackNumBreakpoint@ attacks.

Recommended users: Bel'Veth and Kai'sa
items.name: Adrenaline Modules

items.desc:
Gain @TFTUnitProperty.item:TFT16_Void_IronCarapaceHealth@ max Health. Gain Armor and Magic Resist equal to @TFTUnitProperty.item:TFT16_Void_IronCarapaceArmorMR@% of max Health.

Recommended users: Cho'Gath and Rift Herald
items.name: Iron Carapace

items.desc:
After dealing @DamageRequirement@ damage, fire spikes at the @NumTargets@ nearest enemies that deal @TFTUnitProperty.item:TFT16_Void_SpitterSpinesDamage@ physical damage.

Recommended users: Rek'Sai, Malzahar, and Kai'sa
items.name: Spitter Spines

items.desc:
Gain @TFTUnitProperty.item:TFT16_Void_RoyalHuskHealth@ Health. After dropping below @FirstHealthThreshold*100@% max Health, spawn a Voidling with @TFTUnitProperty.item:TFT16_Void_RoyalHuskSummonMaxHealth@% of this unit's max Health.

Recommended users: Cho'Gath and Rift Herald
items.name: Royal Husk

items.desc:
Heal the lowest Health ally for @TFTUnitProperty.item:TFT16_Void_LeechingHealPercent@% of damage dealt. After damaging an enemy, steal @TFTUnitProperty.item:TFT16_Void_LeechingADAP@% Attack Damage and Ability Power from them, up to @MaxADAPSteal@ stacks from all sources.

Recommended users: Kog'Maw, Malzahar, and Kai'sa
